[{"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "尤蒂爾，稍微在這附近晃一下再回去吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "好啊。偶爾悠閒地散步也……咦……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "！！　蘭薩弗，那個人……！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……………………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "站在懸崖邊，望著遠方……她該不會要……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "……人生到底是什麼……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0037.wav"], "content": "喂喂喂……！她剛剛說了不太妙的話耶！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "嗯，蘭薩弗！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "交給我！等一下──！！別想不開啊──！！　嗚喔喔喔喔喔喔喔喔喔喔喔喔喔喔！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "啊！好漂亮的蝴蝶！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0055.wav", "vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "啊？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "喔，好痛……小姐，妳別想不開啊……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "咦？想不開是指什麼事情呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "說是指什麼……還不就是看妳要跳下去的樣子我才趕來這裡的嗎。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0047.wav"], "content": "對不起，害你們誤會了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "原來只是在看風景啊。聽到妳小聲地說了些意有所指的話，嚇了我一跳。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "妳應該是碰到了什麼事情吧？不介意的話，可以說來聽聽嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "……我叫莎尼亞，是個魔法使。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "過去我和經營南瓜農場的弟弟住一起，但因為他結了婚，趁這個機會我就跑出來旅行了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "喔，弟弟結婚後妳不習慣新家人嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "不是，不是這個原因。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "父母去世後，我一直照顧著弟弟……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0020.wav"], "content": "但弟弟的妻子真的太賢慧了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "該不會是因為自己沒事做了……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "是的……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "所以才會覺得迷惘。想著「我的人生到底是什麼」。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "原來如此，是喪失目標啊。所以才踏上尋找自我之旅吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "可以這麼說……吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我現在想在旅途中，完成父親寫到一半的書。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "是那本書嗎？我看看，「對生活有幫助的魔法事典」？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "莎尼亞的父親是魔法使？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "是的，他是公家機關的魔法使，用魔法進行治水工程或是代理醫師。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "他希望自己的魔法知識能為大家做出貢獻，所以才整理出這本書，但在完成前他就去世了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0020.wav"], "content": "這本書包含許多父親獨家的魔法點子，是很有趣的書，但內容還不夠充實……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "所以我才決定自己試著補足內容，完成父親的書。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "妳真是個孝順的好女兒啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "我沒這麼厲害。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0060.wav"], "content": "我是因為看到書的開頭寫了這一句話，所以才想要試著寫看看。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「人生是為了和平而戰」……說得真好啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "但我父親只是普通的公務員，從沒聽說過他參加戰爭。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "嗯，那麼他為什麼會留下這句話呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "總覺得只要完成這本書，或許就能找到答案。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "我也能找到我的人生目標。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0027.wav"], "content": "原來如此啊。不管怎麼說有目標是件好事。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "沒錯。我們在這裡相遇也是有緣，如果有什麼可以協助的地方請儘管說。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "那麼……如果您知道的話請告訴我。這附近聽說有為了和平而獻身之人。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "如果待在那個人身邊，也許我可以理解父親的話中之意。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那個人似乎叫做尤蒂爾，請將他所在之處──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "──！？哈哈哈哈，這還真是有緣啊！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "似乎是這樣呢。請多指教囉，莎尼亞！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦？咦咦？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110004011, "title": "我的人生究竟是什麼？"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0055.wav"], "content": "菜刀啊！變熱吧！嘿～～～！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "……好了，這樣加熱消毒就完成了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0005.wav"], "content": "真是幫了大忙，最近食物中毒實在太恐怖了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "喔～我都不知道炎之魔法還有這種用法。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "這是父親想出來的魔法活用妙招。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "不過調整威力需要一點技巧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0009.wav"], "content": "莎尼亞，可以麻煩一下嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "槍尖有點鈍了，但是我現在立刻就想用……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "應急處理嗎？我知道了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……把魔力集中在指尖的一點。描過刀刃，用熱稍微熔化它。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "喔喔！幫大忙了！真是感謝！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "那個魔法也是莎尼亞父親的點子嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1001.wav"], "content": "他的點子都很有趣耶。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "呵呵，謝謝你。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "所以我才會對他居然會留下「人生是為了和平而戰」這句話感到不可思議。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "來到這裡後，雖然有各種機會可以嘗試父親的魔法，", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "但卻完全找不到答案。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "唔……和平是什麼？父親的人生是什麼？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "而我的人生又是什麼……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "好了好了，這樣鑽牛角尖也沒用。慢慢來就好。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "沒錯。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "胡思亂想也只是搞得自己頭痛，像這時候最好喧鬧一番發洩一下。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "蘭薩弗……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "所以啊，莎尼亞。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "你父親的點子裡，有沒有可以用在宴會特技表演的構想？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "咦？那個……沒有在宴會表演用的魔法……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "不會吧，一個都沒有嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "我跟村民們說好要表演新特技了！拜託！　", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "蘭薩弗，強人所難不太……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0034.wav"], "content": "怎麼會強人所難！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "要吸引目光並博得滿堂喝彩的話，一定要有特技表演！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "……那我幫你