peakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0045.wav"], "content": "莎尼亞，謝謝妳。這樣就能稍微和平一點了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0020.wav"], "content": "啊哈哈……「為了和平而戰」就是這個意思吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "我猜不是這樣的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110004012, "title": "為和平而戰可不容易"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0076.wav"], "content": "就是這傢伙吧！？　襲擊郵務馬車的魔獸！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "莎尼亞，麻煩掩護我！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "好的！炎之藤蔓啊，守護他吧──！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0055.wav"], "content": "喝啊啊啊啊啊啊！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "被搶走的包裹全都在這了吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "嗯？這封信是要送到我們城裡的。寄信人是……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "啊──！！那封信！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "是莎尼亞啊？妳在這裡做什麼？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "啊，尤蒂爾。我在讀信。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "是故鄉的弟弟寄來的？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "是的。信裡提到今年南瓜應該會大豐收。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "還有就是不斷在誇讚自己的妻子……呵呵！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "感覺妳很開心呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "是既開心，又寂寞。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……因為弟弟做事總是粗心大意，沒有我就不行，才一直努力照顧他。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "但是之後卻娶了個可愛的妻子喔？　", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "我真是嚇了一跳。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那時候我開始覺得「他長大了」。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "「就算我不在也沒關係」。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "而且弟媳為弟弟犧牲奉獻支持著他，是個非常好的女孩。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "就連我也喜歡上她了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "但是，我發覺這麼一來，我就失去繼續努力的理由了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "所以才會喪失目標嗎。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0020.wav"], "content": "啊哈哈，有一段時間還打算專心培育從以前就很喜歡的家庭菜園，但總覺得有點不踏實。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "然後有一天，我在整理菜園的農舍時偶然發現了這本書。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "我不知道為什麼父親的遺物會被丟置在那裡。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但如果沒發現這本書，我現在應該還是沒有任何目標吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "妳父親是什麼樣的人？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "是個普通的公務員喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "個性有點爛好人，到處都有人拜託他做一堆事情。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "還有，他在放假時會教我魔法。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "我現在會使用魔法，都是多虧了父親的指導。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "……也許這本書是故意只寫到一半的吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "妳父親可能已經預測到妳弟弟結婚後，妳會開始對人生感到迷惘吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "怎麼可能！？父親為什麼可以想像到現在的我？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "因為妳個性認真，又很會照顧人啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "所以才準備了照顧弟弟以外的事情，讓妳有個目標吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "所以他才準備這本未完成的書？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "是為了讓喪失目標的我能再度振作，才為我準備了完成這本書的目標嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "我覺得書會放在菜園的農舍裡，就是因為只有妳會找到。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……不過這只是我的想像。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "不……或許你說得對。因為父親他很溫柔……呵呵呵！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110004013, "title": "收到弟弟的來信了"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "父親的遺物……「對生活有幫助的魔法事典」……終於完成了…………唉。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "感覺妳沒什麼精神呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "結果即使完成了我還是不了解。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "父親的「人生是為了和平而戰」這句話的意思。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "也沒找到……我的人生目標……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "完成這本書後，我到底要怎麼辦才好呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "……唉～～～！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "唔……又喪失目標了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "糟糕了！耶魯菲莉絲她──！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "接到村民的委託，耶魯菲莉絲前去討伐棲息在森林裡的魔獸。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "然後……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "魔獸裡有會使用毒針的魔獸。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我一時大意中了那傢伙的攻擊……咕……呼、呼、呼……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "她說這委託不需要麻煩尤蒂爾動手，都怪她耍帥自己一個人去……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0037.wav"], "content": "毒針留在體內的深處。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "如果不把毒針取出來，就算我使用回復魔法也沒有意義。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1011.wav"], "content": "……只能開刀了嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "而且還要盡快，沒有時間叫醫生了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "我們之中有誰能進行這麼細膩的技術？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "要是沒處理好，可是會在還沒出嫁的女孩身上留下疤痕喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "唔！要是能只破壞毒針就好了……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0054.wav"], "content": "！！或許辦得到！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "父親的書裡有記載如何調整炎之魔法的威力，還有將魔力集中在一點的方法！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "只要應用這些方法，就能在不開刀的情況下，把體內的毒針燒掉！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0027.wav"], "content": "原來如此！以最小火力的炎之魔法從傷口燒向毒針啊！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "或許行得通！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我們之中只有妳辦得到，妳願意幫忙嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "好的！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "……耶魯菲莉絲睡得很熟。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "明天早上起床時，應該就會恢復精神了吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0046.wav"], "content": "莎尼亞，謝謝妳救了耶魯菲莉絲。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "我、我沒做什麼大不了的事，因為有父親的書，我才能辦到。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "不，空有知識什麼也辦不到。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "都是因為有妳的新發現，所以才能做到的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "新發現……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "書中記載的其他魔法，也能依照應用方法的不同，而產生無限的可能性吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "雖然書已經完成了，但應該還是有很多能做的事情不是嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "說得也是，我會再試著努力一下！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110004_01.png", "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110004014, "title": "續‧我的人生究竟是什麼？"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "尤蒂爾，這裡也有！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "就跟克菈兒說得一樣，這附近是藥草的寶庫啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "多摘一點回去吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120020_story/VO_CHR_120020_STORY_0065.wav"], "content": "哎呀？妳該不會是莎尼亞吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "老婆婆", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦？是以前住在隔壁的婆婆？　", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "好久不見了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120020_story/VO_CHR_120020_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "妳也來這採藥草啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "老婆婆", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這麼說來，這裡曾經是妳父親守護的地方啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "老婆婆", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦？什麼意思？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120020_story/VO_CHR_120020_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "哎呀，妳不知道嗎？　", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "老婆婆", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這裡的藥草以前差點全死光了。每次只要下雨，附近的河川就會氾濫。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "老婆婆", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "然後妳父親用魔法進行了治水工程。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "老婆婆", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "多虧他，藥草才沒有滅絕喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "老婆婆", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120020_story/VO_CHR_120020_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "但聽說那道工程很辛苦。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "老婆婆", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "你父親不斷反覆試驗了好幾次。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "老婆婆", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "……我都不知道。因為父親他都不太談工作。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120020_story/VO_CHR_120020_STORY_0021.wav"], "content": "之前得了致死的重病，也因為有這裡的藥草才能輕易治好，真是得救了啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "老婆婆", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "還不只這樣。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "老婆婆", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "河川不再氾濫後，下游的村子也不需要擔心水災了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "老婆婆", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "非常活躍呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "因為有妳的父親，大家才能安心的生活啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "老婆婆", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120020_story/VO_CHR_120020_STORY_0046.wav"], "content": "有他的努力，才建立了和平的基礎呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "老婆婆", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "莎尼亞的父親真的曾經奮戰過呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不過並不是拿劍戰鬥……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "而是不斷費心與努力，為大家建立和平、守護和平而奮戰。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "那就是他的人生，所以書的開頭才會寫著──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "「人生是為了和平而戰」。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "呵呵。為大家而戰，還為我留下了遺物……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "真是個好父親啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……尤蒂爾，我決定了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "我要繼續研究魔法。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不只組合父親的魔法，我還要研發自己的新魔法。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "然後把那些新魔法加到父親的書裡，傳給下個世代。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "這樣才算完成這本書。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "妳找到自己的人生目標了呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110004_story/VO_CHR_110004_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "是的。為開拓和平之路而戰。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那就是生為溫柔又有尊嚴的魔法使之女……我的人生！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "莎尼亞", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110004015, "title": "這才是我的人生！"}]